{"tid":1305360,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"關於本地運動打氣或支持的歌曲","createTime":"2019-07-10T23:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T10:53:04.000Z","uid":15341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ac25c929ab726dcd46d4a408dde714726f67204","tid":1305360,"uid":15341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T23:47:02.000Z","msg":"經歷了這段時間，聽過不少容支持或打氣的歌<br />\n大部份都係群星合唱，舒情慢歌，感覺上是代表了很多和理非的人<br />\n然而我覺得咁樣嘅歌曲欠缺士氣或激情<br />\n若果有Rock 嘅完素會大大提高士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比較岩勇武<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\nOne Ok Rock - The Beginning <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/4f3nDjgqXurMryYBSp0TZD?si=yRHgvxhtQwmvBIVVp52v9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Ftrack%2F4f3nDjgqXurMryYBSp0TZD%3Fsi%3DyRHgvxhtQwmvBIVVp52v9A&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJndDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=a91a8ec5\" target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/track/4f3nDjgqXurMryYBSp0TZD?si=yRHgvxhtQwmvBIVVp52v9A</a><br />\n<br />\nSum 41 - Still Waiting<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/4rLKjYqJjLU0Odg52kGL2O?si=TkGqc6xNRcSz9a9ep5-joQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Ftrack%2F4rLKjYqJjLU0Odg52kGL2O%3Fsi%3DTkGqc6xNRcSz9a9ep5-joQ&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJndDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=41552511\" target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/track/4rLKjYqJjLU0Odg52kGL2O?si=TkGqc6xNRcSz9a9ep5-joQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家細心留意下啲歌詞都幾表達到心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家都覺得岩聽嘅，我會再不停搵黎分享俾大家<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家記得5大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8aa5e4c359abf8e0710711c7e54a2a14b86c5e","tid":1305360,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:43:21.000Z","msg":"有無人整咗 「反送中 Playlist」？"},{"pid":"a6f32c48645dabd5ec9f4a06bb42467f46a1b37d","tid":1305360,"uid":15341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc8aa5e4c359abf8e0710711c7e54a2a14b86c5e","tid":1305360,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:43:21.000Z","msg":"有無人整咗 「反送中 Playlist」？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"如果真係覺得岩嘅，我會整理返個playlist <br />\n<br />\n因為下下都舒情歌，真係提唔到太多士氣<br />\n每個人對音樂要求唔同，我唔係話舒情歌唔好<br />\n不過我只係想有啲轉變"},{"pid":"a01fa14e174d830e6095ea564bb5cb3da0f0ad9a","tid":1305360,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc8aa5e4c359abf8e0710711c7e54a2a14b86c5e","tid":1305360,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:43:21.000Z","msg":"有無人整咗 「反送中 Playlist」？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:59:23.000Z","msg":"Spotify有"},{"pid":"216352d53ba1b2534e03a565fd4e8b7eb121dc84","tid":1305360,"uid":15341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a01fa14e174d830e6095ea564bb5cb3da0f0ad9a","tid":1305360,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc8aa5e4c359abf8e0710711c7e54a2a14b86c5e","tid":1305360,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:43:21.000Z","msg":"有無人整咗 「反送中 Playlist」？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:59:23.000Z","msg":"Spotify有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:53:04.000Z","msg":"主打廣東歌<br />\n不過我都想整個外語版playlist 出黎"}]}